commit.message: Set the parent class to IBusEngineSimple.
Removed accept-focus property on ibus-setup-input-pad dialog.
Showed custom table only by default.
Changed the engine layout from 'us' to 'default'.

Ported to GTK+ 3.10 to fix the deprecated APIs.

GtkTable        -> GtkGrid
GtkVBox         -> GtkBox
GtkHButtonBox   -> GtkButtonBox
Changed the static GtkBuilder file to the resource file.
Changed set_logo_name to set_logo in GtkAboutDialog.
Deprecated GtkStock
Renamed setup gtk2 files to gtk ones to support gtk3 only.

Released 1.4.2

Removed shared_type tag in input-pad.xml, which is not upstreamed.

Released 1.4.1

Added ibus-setup-input-pad.desktop
Enabled GTK3 by default.
